729283f-a.folder: Poplar Street & Rossville Avenue, Staten Island, NY
729283f-a.text:
(1) Poplar Street, adjoining the S.W. corner of Roseville Avenue, showing St. Josephs Roman Catholic Church. April 30, 1929.  P. L. Sperr

(2) A view of the church (left) and the rectory. The rectory adjoins the church on the west. April 30, 1929. P. L. Sperr

(3) The rectory, eight years later, showing alterations. May 5, 1937. P. L. Sperr
